In the “Withholding Tax Certificates Setup (ECU)” page, two actions are available:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000298-0/setup ecu en.png"><br>



**Recalculate Wihholding Non-taxable Amounts** used to realign situations where the ECU detail tables for non-taxable amounts are inconsistent with the original data.


**Check Withholding Non Taxable Amounts** analyzes all processed withholding entries and checks that the standard field is consistent with the sum of the amounts in the ECU detail tables. If inconsistencies are found, it generates an Excel file listing the documents with mismatches, which is useful to identify where to intervene before running the recalculation.